It happens so often that I have a macro for thanking people for a rezz.<br>
<br>
I also have a couple of others that I find useful<br>
<br>
/g Mob charmed for 18 seconds<br>
/g pet attack %t<br>
<br>
and<br>
<br>
/g Breaking charm in 5. Aggro cleared...<br>
/g ...except for me...ouchy, ouchy.<br>
<br>
Sometimes when someone is screwing up badly and you're playing a bard it's a case of flipping the coin between stuffing your twist to correct them or keeping the mobs mezz/snared and hoping they don't do it again.<br>
